graph TD
    subgraph Live Inputs
        MIC[Vocal Mic] --> CH1[Ch1 Vocal Dry<br/>GATE dynamics]
        DI[Guitar DI] --> CH2[Ch2 Guitar Dry]
    end

    subgraph Vocal Outboard Chain - Patchbay P1-P4
        CH1 -->|Bus 1 Vocal Send<br/>pre-fader, clean| OUT1[Wing Out 1 → P1]
        OUT1 --> HA73A[HA73 A<br/>Neve EQ / Color]
        HA73A -->|P2| WA76A[WA76 A<br/>1176 Compression<br/>Atk 3, Rel 7, 4:1]
        WA76A -->|P3| OPTO[Opto<br/>LA-2A Leveling<br/>Peak Red ~40%]
        OPTO -->|P4| CH17[Ch17 Vocal Processed<br/>DE-ES dynamics]
    end

    subgraph Guitar Amp Sim Stage
        CH2 -->|pre-fader| BUS5[Bus 5 Electric<br/>FX6 ANGEL lead /<br/>FX1 DELUXE rhythm]
        CH2 -->|pre-fader| BUS6[Bus 6 Acoustic<br/>FX11 RACKAMP clean]
        BUS5 -->|send| BUS2[Bus 2 Guitar Send<br/>clean to outboard]
        BUS6 -->|send| BUS2
    end

    subgraph Guitar Outboard Chain - Patchbay P5-P8
        BUS2 --> OUT2[Wing Out 2 → P5]
        OUT2 --> HA73B[HA73 B<br/>Neve EQ / Color]
        HA73B -->|P6| WA76B[WA76 B<br/>1176 Compression<br/>Atk 5, Rel 6, 4:1]
        WA76B -->|P7| DIST[Distressor<br/>Leveling + Tape Sat<br/>4:1, Dist 2]
        DIST -->|P8| CH18[Ch18 Guitar Processed]
    end

    subgraph Recording Path - to Logic
        CH17 -->|Bus 7 Vocal Rec send<br/>pre-fader| BUS7[Bus 7 Vocal Rec<br/>FX9 TAPE]
        CH18 -->|Bus 8 Guitar Rec send<br/>pre-fader| BUS8[Bus 8 Guitar Rec<br/>FX10 TAPE]
        BUS7 -->|USB| LOGIC[Logic Pro<br/>Primary Recorder]
        BUS8 -->|USB / Out 3 analog| LOGIC
    end

    subgraph Monitoring - to Main 1
        CH17 -->|assigned to main| MAIN[Main 1<br/>Headphones / Speakers]
        CH18 --> BUS10[Bus 10 Gtr Rhythm Mon<br/>RACKAMP]
        CH18 --> BUS11[Bus 11 Gtr Lead Mon<br/>ANGEL]
        BUS10 --> MAIN
        BUS11 --> MAIN
    end

    subgraph Tape Returns - Logic Playback
        LOGIC -->|USB 17-26| TR[Ch25-32 Tape Returns<br/>per-track bus sends]
        TR -->|Bus 3 Reverb| BUS3[Bus 3 Reverb<br/>FX2 PLATE]
        TR -->|Bus 10/11 for guitar| BUS10B[Bus 10 Rhythm /<br/>Bus 11 Lead]
        BUS3 --> MAIN
        BUS10B --> MAIN
        TR -->|direct| MAIN
    end

    subgraph Session Players
        SP[Logic Session Players<br/>Bass, Keys, Synth, Drums] -->|USB 9-16| CH9[Ch9-12] --> MAIN
    end

    NOTE[Recording captures: gate + outboard + de-esser + tape.<br/>Monitoring adds: amp sim + reverb.<br/>Tape returns play back through the same FX buses.<br/>All paths run simultaneously - no mode switching.]

